title._content: Rune stones and bucket, Orlunda Churchyard, Östergötland, Sweden

description._content: Rune stone fragments (Ög 5, 6) at Orlunda churchyard, and a bucket. The inscription on the larger rune stone says: "(N.N. placed) this (stone) in memory of Åsa, his wife". Runstensfragment (Ög 5, 6) på Orlunda kyrkogård, och en hink. Ristningen på den större runstenen säger: "(N.N. lade) denna (sten) efter Åsa, sin hustru". Parish (socken): Orlunda Province (landskap): Östergötland Municipality (kommun): Vadstena County (län): Östergötland Photograph by: Unknown Date: c. 1900 Format: Glass plate negative Persistent URL: http://www.kms.raa.se/cocoon/bild/show-image.html?id=16001000188324 Read more about the photo database (in english): www.kms.raa.se/cocoon/bild/about.html
